msgid "Bland-Altman Plots"
msgstr "Gráficos de Bland-Altman"

msgid ""
"Bland-Altman plots of the mean vs. difference for each variable pair, with "
"mean difference and limits of agreement."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Scatter plot of mean vs. difference of the two measurements. The middle "
"dashed line is the mean difference (bias); the outer dashed lines are the "
"limits of agreement (±1.96 SD)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Please provide another variable"
msgstr "Por favor, indica otra variable"

msgid "Plotting not possible: %s"
msgstr "No es posible hacer el gráfico: %s"

msgid "Bland-Altman Tables"
msgstr "Tablas de Bland-Altman"

msgid ""
"Summary statistics for each pair: bias (mean difference), limits of "
"agreement, and optional confidence intervals."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Mean difference (bias), lower and upper limits of agreement for this pair. "
"If confidence intervals are requested, uncertainty bounds for each limit are "
"also shown."
msgstr ""

msgid "Bias & Limits"
msgstr "Sesgo & Límites"

msgid "Point Value"
msgstr "Valor Puntual"

msgid "Mean difference - 1.96 SD"
msgstr "Diferencia media - 1.96 DT"

msgid "Mean difference + 1.96 SD"
msgstr "Diferencia media + 1.96 DT"

msgid "Mean difference"
msgstr "Diferencia de Medias"

msgid "Lower %s%% CI"
msgstr "IC inferior al %s%%"

msgid "Upper %s%% CI"
msgstr "IC superior %s%%"

msgid "Calculations not possible: %s"
msgstr "Los cálculos no son posibles: %s"

msgid "Intraclass Correlation"
msgstr "Correlación intraclase"

msgid ""
"Intraclass correlation coefficients (ICC) with optional confidence intervals "
"for assessing absolute agreement or consistency among raters."
msgstr ""

msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tipo"

msgid "Point Estimate"
msgstr "Estimación por Punto"

msgid ""
"%1$s subjects and %2$s raters/measurements. ICC type as referenced by Shrout "
"& Fleiss (1979)."
msgstr ""
"%1$s sujetos y %2$s calificadores/medidas. Tipo de CCI según la referencia "
"de Shrout & Fleiss (1979)."

msgid "Please select at least 2 columns"
msgstr "Por favor seleccione al menos 2 columnas"

#, fuzzy
msgid "Agreement Coefficient"
msgstr "Coeficiente"

msgid ""
"Empty placeholder table shown while no agreement coefficient is selected; "
"check a coefficient to obtain results."
msgstr ""

msgid "Coefficient"
msgstr "Coeficiente"

msgid "Estimate"
msgstr "Estimar"

msgid "SE"
msgstr "ET"

msgid "Lower"
msgstr "Inferior"

msgid "Upper"
msgstr "Superior"

msgid "Check one of the coefficients to start the analysis."
msgstr ""

msgid "%s%% CI"
msgstr "IC del %s%%"

msgid ""
"%s requires a common ordinal scale, but the declared category orders of the "
"raters are contradictory or do not determine a unique order. Ensure all "
"raters use the same ordered categories."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"With raters in rows, all subject/item columns must have the same measurement "
"type. The data mix categorical and continuous columns; change the column "
"types so they match."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Krippendorff's alpha requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "La kappa de Fleiss requiere al menos 2 evaluadores/medidas."

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha with an interval or ratio method requires numeric "
"ratings. Use the nominal or ordinal method, or recode the data."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha with the ratio method requires non-negative ratings."
msgstr ""

msgid "Krippendorff's alpha with the ordinal method"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha cannot be computed: the data contain infinite values."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha cannot be computed: no subject/item was rated by at "
"least 2 raters (no pairable observations)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha is not estimable: the pairable ratings do not vary."
msgstr ""

msgid "Cohen's kappa"
msgstr "Kappa de Cohen"

msgid ""
"Cohen's kappa: chance-corrected agreement between exactly two raters. Ranges "
"from -1 (worse than chance) to 1 (perfect agreement)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Ratings"
msgstr "Calificaciones"

msgid "kappa"
msgstr "Kappa"

msgid ""
"Cohen's kappa requires nominal or ordinal variables. Remove scale variables "
"or change their type."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Weighted Cohen's kappa requires ordinal variables. Remove nominal variables "
"or change their type."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Cohen's kappa requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "La kappa de Fleiss requiere al menos 2 evaluadores/medidas."

#, fuzzy
msgid "Weighted Cohen's kappa"
msgstr "Kappa de Cohen"

msgid "fewer than 3 jointly rated subjects/items"
msgstr ""

msgid "the ratings do not vary"
msgstr ""

msgid "the coefficient is not estimable"
msgstr ""

msgid "Cohen's kappa could not be computed for any rater pair: %s."
msgstr ""

msgid "Some rater pairs could not be computed:"
msgstr ""

msgid ". They are excluded from the average kappa."
msgstr ""

msgid "Note:"
msgstr ""

msgid "%1$i subjects/items and %2$i raters/measurements."
msgstr "%1$i sujetos/elementos y %2$i calificadores/medidas."

msgid "%1$s Based on pairwise complete cases."
msgstr "%1$s Basado en casos completos por pares."

msgid "n"
msgstr ""

msgid "Confidence intervals are asymptotic."
msgstr "Los intervalos de confianza son asintóticos."

msgid ""
"If there are only 2 levels, weighted kappa is equal to unweighted kappa."
msgstr "Si solo hay 2 niveles, kappa ponderada equivale a kappa sin ponderar."

msgid "Cohen's kappa requires at least 3 subjects/items."
msgstr "La kappa de Cohen requiere al menos 3 sujetos/elementos."

msgid "Fleiss' kappa"
msgstr "Kappa de Fleiss"

msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa: generalization of Cohen's kappa for two or more raters "
"assigning subjects to nominal categories."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa requires nominal or ordinal variables. Remove scale variables "
"or change their type."
msgstr ""

msgid "Fleiss' kappa requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "La kappa de Fleiss requiere al menos 2 evaluadores/medidas."

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa requires at least 3 complete subjects/items (rows without "
"missing ratings). Check whether raters are in columns or rows."
msgstr ""
"La kappa de Fleiss requiere al menos 3 sujetos/elementos. Comprueba si los "
"evaluadores están en columnas o filas."

msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa is not estimable: all ratings fall into a single category."
msgstr ""

msgid "%1$s Based on listwise complete cases."
msgstr "%1$s Basado en casos completos por lista."

msgid "Krippendorff's alpha"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha: reliability coefficient applicable to any number of "
"raters, any scale level (nominal/ordinal/interval/ratio), and incomplete "
"data."
msgstr ""

msgid "Method"
msgstr "Método"

msgid "Krippendorff's alpha is not estimable for these data."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"%1$i of %2$i bootstrap samples could not be computed and were excluded from "
"the CI."
msgstr ""

msgid "Kendall's W"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Kendall's coefficient of concordance W: measures agreement of rankings "
"across multiple raters. Ranges from 0 (no agreement) to 1 (perfect "
"concordance). Significance is assessed with the large-sample chi-square test "
"and the F test, which performs better for small samples."
msgstr ""

msgid "Chi-square test"
msgstr ""

msgid "F test"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Kendall's W requires ordinal or scale variables. Remove nominal variables."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Kendall's W requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "La kappa de Fleiss requiere al menos 2 evaluadores/medidas."

msgid ""
"Kendall's W requires at least 2 complete subjects/items (rows without "
"missing ratings)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Kendall's W cannot be computed: the data contain infinite values."
msgstr ""

msgid "Kendall's W is not estimable: the rankings do not vary."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Bootstrap CIs are only available with the tie correction enabled: resampling "
"with replacement introduces ties, which distort the uncorrected coefficient."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Confidence intervals are based on bootstrap."
msgstr "Los intervalos de confianza son asintóticos."

msgid "Chi-square test is valid for large samples only."
msgstr ""

msgid "The F test is undefined for perfect concordance (W = 1)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The F test is not available for this design: it requires n - 1 - 2/m > 0 (n "
"= subjects/items, m = raters)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Ties are present in the ratings, so the uncorrected coefficient may be "
"inaccurate. Consider enabling the tie correction."
msgstr ""

msgid "Warning:"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"For the Lord generalized method, the test could not be split in equally "
"sized parts with more than 1 item per part. Consider adding or removing "
"items."
msgstr ""
"Para el método generalizado de Lord, el contraste no pudo dividirse en "
"partes de igual tamaño con más de un elemento por parte. Considere añadir o "
"eliminar elementos."

msgid "Standard error of measurement results for the selected methods."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The Lord, Keats, and Lord generalized method are only available for binary "
"data."
msgstr ""
"El método generalizado de Lord, Keats e Lord está disponible solo para datos "
"binarios."

msgid "Standard Error of Measurement"
msgstr "Error típico de la medida"

msgid ""
"Conditional standard error of measurement (SEM) for each sum score using the "
"selected method(s). The unconditional SEM is also shown."
msgstr ""

msgid "Sum Score"
msgstr "Suma puntuación"

msgid "Unconditional SEM"
msgstr "ETM (SEM) no condicionado"

msgid "Counts"
msgstr "Recuentos"

msgid "%1$s The unconditional SEM value equals %2$1.3f."
msgstr "%1$s El valor del ETM (MES) no condicionado es igual a %2$1.3f."

msgid ""
"%1$s Estimating the %2$s method failed. If possible, you might try changing "
"the method's parameters."
msgstr ""
"%1$s Falló la estimación del método %2$s. Si es posible, podrías tratar de "
"cambiar los parámetros del método."

msgid "Sum Score CI Table"
msgstr "Tabla de IC suma de puntuaciones"

msgid ""
"Confidence intervals for the true score at each sum score level, computed "
"from the conditional SEM."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Estimating the %s method failed. If possible, you might try changing the "
"method's parameters."
msgstr ""
"Falló la estimación del método %s. Si es posible, podrías tratar de cambiar "
"los parámetros del método."

msgid "Histogram of Counts per Sum Score Group"
msgstr "Histograma de recuentos por grupo de suma de puntuaciones"

msgid "Distribution of participants across sum score groups."
msgstr ""

msgid "Point Plots"
msgstr "Gráficos de puntos"

msgid ""
"Conditional SEM plotted as a function of sum score for each selected method."
msgstr ""

msgid "SEM"
msgstr "M.E.S."

msgid "Combined Plot"
msgstr "Gráfico combinado"

msgid ""
"Overlay of all selected methods' conditional SEM across the full range of "
"sum scores."
msgstr ""

msgid "Sum Score CI Plots"
msgstr "Gráficos de IC de suma de puntuación"

msgid ""
"True-score confidence interval plotted against sum score for each selected "
"method."
msgstr ""

msgid "True Score Estimate"
msgstr "Estimación de la puntuación correcta"

msgid "Split-half coefficient"
msgstr "Coeficiente de división en mitades"

msgid "Item-rest correlation"
msgstr "Correlación del elemento con el resto"

msgid "Mean"
msgstr "Media"

msgid "Variance"
msgstr "Varianza"

msgid "SD"
msgstr "DT"

msgid "%1$s Of the observations, %2$1.f complete cases were used."
msgstr "%1$s de las observaciones, se utilizaron %2$1.f casos completos."

msgid "%s Of the observations, pairwise complete cases were used."
msgstr "%s de las observaciones, se utilizaron casos completos por pares."

msgid ""
"Sampling the posterior covariance matrix for either one of [alpha, lambda2, "
"lambda6, glb] failed. Try changing to 'Exclude cases listwise' in 'Advanced "
"Options'"
msgstr ""
"Falló el muestreo de la matriz posterior de covarianzas para alguno de estos "
"[alpha, lambda2, lambda6, glb]. Intenta cambiar a 'Excluir casos según "
"lista' en 'Opciones Avanzadas '"

msgid ""
"Sampling the posterior covariance matrix for either one of [alpha, lambda2, "
"lambda6, glb] failed."
msgstr ""
"Falló el muestreo de la matriz posterior de covarianzas para alguno de estos "
"[alpha, lambda2, lambda6, glb]."

msgid ""
"Sampling the posterior factor model for omega failed. Try changing to "
"'Exclude cases listwise' in 'Advanced Options'"
msgstr ""
"Falló el muestreo del modelo posterior de factores para omega. Intenta "
"cambiar a 'Excluir casos según lista' en 'Opciones Avanzadas '"

msgid ""
"Sampling the posterior null model failed. Try changing to 'Exclude cases "
"listwise' in 'Advanced Options'"
msgstr ""
"Falló el muestreo del modelo nulo posterior. Intenta cambiar a 'Excluir "
"casos según lista' en 'Opciones Avanzadas '"

msgid "Bayesian Scale Reliability Statistics"
msgstr "Estadísticas de confiabilidad de escala bayesiana"

msgid ""
"Bayesian posterior estimates and credible intervals for all selected scale "
"reliability coefficients."
msgstr ""

msgid "Posterior %s"
msgstr "%s posterior"

msgid "R-hat"
msgstr "R-circunflejo"

msgid "ESS"
msgstr "SCR"

msgid "Bayesian Individual Item Reliability Statistics"
msgstr "Estadísticas bayesianas de confiabilidad de ítems individuales"

msgid ""
"Bayesian item-level reliability: posterior estimates of the scale "
"coefficient if each item were dropped, and item-rest correlations."
msgstr ""

msgid "Item"
msgstr "Ítem"

msgid "%s (if item dropped)"
msgstr "%s (si ítem eliminado)"

msgid ""
"%s Please enter at least 3 variables for the if item dropped statistics."
msgstr ""
"%s Por favor, introduzca al menos 3 variables para las estadísticas de "
"eliminación de los ítems."

msgid ""
"The bounds you entered have been rearranged in increasing order to provide "
"meaningful results."
msgstr ""
"Los límites que has indicado se volvieron a colocar en orden creciente para "
"proporcionar resultados comprensibles."

msgid ""
"Probability that Reliability Coefficient is Larger than %1$.2f and Smaller "
"than %2$.2f"
msgstr ""
"Probabilidad de que el estadístico de confiabilidad sea mayor que %1$.2f y "
"menor que %2$.2f"

msgid ""
"Posterior and prior probability that each reliability coefficient falls "
"within the specified interval."
msgstr ""

msgid "Probability"
msgstr "Probabilidad"

msgid "Prior"
msgstr "Previo"

msgid "Posterior"
msgstr "Posterior"

msgid "Fit Measures for the Single-Factor Model"
msgstr "Medidas de Ajuste del Modelo de Factor Único"

msgid ""
"Bayesian fit indices for the single-factor model underlying McDonald's omega."
msgstr ""

msgid "%s lower bound"
msgstr "%s límite inferior"

msgid "%s upper bound"
msgstr "%s límite superior"

msgid ""
"'Relative to cutoff'-row denotes the probability that the B-RMSEA is smaller "
"than\n"
"                         the corresponding cutoff and the probabilities that "
"the B-CFI/TLI are larger than the\n"
"                         corresponding cutoff."
msgstr ""
"La fila 'Relativo al punto de corte' expresa la probabilidad de que la B-"
"REACM sea menor que\n"
"                         el punto de corte correspondiente, y las "
"probabilidades de que los B-IAC/ITL sean mayores que\n"
"                         el punto de corte correspondiente."

msgid "Standardized Loadings of the Single-Factor Model"
msgstr "Cargas Tipificadas del Modelo de Factor Único"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Posterior estimates of standardized factor loadings from the single-factor "
"model."
msgstr "Cargas Tipificadas del Modelo de Factor Único"

msgid "Standardized loading"
msgstr "Carga tipificada"

msgid "Posterior Plots"
msgstr "Gráficos Posteriores"

msgid ""
"Posterior density plots for each selected reliability coefficient, with "
"optional prior overlay and shading of the posterior probability region; the "
"credible interval is shown as a separate error bar."
msgstr ""

msgid "Density"
msgstr "Densidad"

msgid "If Item Dropped Posterior Plots"
msgstr "Gráficos posteriores si el ítem se eliminó"

msgid ""
"Ridgeline plots showing the posterior distribution of each reliability "
"coefficient when each item is dropped."
msgstr ""

msgid "Please enter at least 3 variables for the if item dropped plot"
msgstr ""
"Por favor, introducir al menos 3 variables para el gráfico al quitar "
"elementos"

msgid "KLD ordering failed because two variables have perfect correlation"
msgstr ""
"El ordenamiento KLD falló porque dos variables tienen una correlación "
"perfecta"

msgid "Item Dropped"
msgstr "Ítem eliminado"

msgid "Eigenvalue"
msgstr "Autovalor"

msgid "Eigenvalue No."
msgstr "Autovalor No."

msgid "Posterior Predictive Check Omega"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Posterior predictive check: observed eigenvalues of the covariance matrix "
"compared against the model-implied posterior distribution to assess single-"
"factor model fit."
msgstr ""

msgid "Convergence Traceplot"
msgstr "Traceplot de convergencia"

msgid ""
"Traceplots of MCMC samples per chain over iterations to assess sampler "
"convergence and mixing."
msgstr ""

msgid "Iterations"
msgstr "Iteraciones"

msgid "Average interitem correlation"
msgstr "Correlación media entre elementos"

msgid "%1$s%2$s"
msgstr "%1$s%2$s"

msgid ""
"Omega calculation with CFA failed.\n"
"                                                    Try changing to PFA in "
"'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"Falló el cálculo de Omega con AFC.\n"
"                                                    Probar a cambiar a AFP "
"en \"Opciones Avanzadas\"."

msgid ""
"Omega bootstrapped interval calculation with CFA failed.\n"
"                                                        Try changing to PFA "
"in 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"Falló el cálculo del intervalo de bootstrapp de Omega con AFC.\n"
"                                                            Probar a cambiar "
"a AFP en \"Opciones Avanzadas\"."

msgid "Omega calculation with PFA failed."
msgstr "Falló el cálculo de Omega con AFP."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval is not available for coefficient omega "
"obtained with PFA. Change to 'Bootstrapped' in Advanced Options."
msgstr ""
"El intervalo analítico de confianza no está disponible para el coeficiente "
"omega obtenido con AFP. Cambia a 'Bootstrap' en Opciones Avanzadas."

msgid "Omega interval calculation with PFA failed."
msgstr "Falló el cálculo del intervalo de Omega con AFP."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval is not available for coefficient alpha/"
"lambda2 when data contain missings and pairwise complete observations are "
"used. Try changing to 'Delete listwise' within 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"El intervalo de confianza analítico no está disponible para el coeficiente "
"alfa/lambda2 cuando los datos contienen valores ausentes y se utilizan "
"observaciones completas por pares. Intente cambiar a 'Eliminar por lista' en "
"'Opciones avanzadas'."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval is not available for the average interitem "
"correlation when data contain missings and pairwise complete observations "
"are used. Try changing to 'Delete listwise' within 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"El intervalo de confianza analítico no está disponible para la correlación "
"media entre elementos cuando los datos contienen valores ausentes y se "
"utilizan observaciones completas por pares. Intente cambiar a 'Eliminar por "
"lista' en 'Opciones avanzadas'."

msgid "Omega item dropped statistics with CFA failed."
msgstr "Fallaron los estadísticos del elemento Omega eliminado con CFA."

msgid "Omega item dropped statistics with PFA failed."
msgstr "Fallaron los estadísticos del elemento Omega eliminado con PFA."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval not available for coefficient alpha/lambda2 "
"when data contain missings and pairwise complete observations are used. Try "
"changing to 'Delete listwise' within 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"El intervalo de confianza analítico no está disponible para el coeficiente "
"alfa/lambda2 cuando los datos contienen valores ausentes y se utilizan "
"observaciones completas por pares. Intente cambiar a 'Eliminar por lista' en "
"'Opciones avanzadas'."

msgid "Frequentist Scale Reliability Statistics"
msgstr "Estadísticas de confiabilidad de la escala frecuente"

msgid ""
"Frequentist point estimates, standard errors, and confidence intervals for "
"all selected scale reliability coefficients."
msgstr ""

msgid "Std. Error"
msgstr "Error típico"

msgid "Frequentist Individual Item Reliability Statistics"
msgstr "Estadísticas de confiabilidad de ítems individuales frecuentes"

msgid ""
"Item-level reliability: for each item, the scale reliability coefficient if "
"that item were dropped, and the item-rest correlation."
msgstr ""

msgid "Fit Measures of Single Factor Model Fit"
msgstr "Medidas de ajuste del modelo de un solo factor"

msgid ""
"Fit indices of the single-factor model underlying McDonald's omega, "
"including chi-square, RMSEA, and SRMR."
msgstr ""

msgid "Fit measure"
msgstr "Medida de ajuste"

msgid "Value"
msgstr "Valor"

